Text:
i prefer, Notepad2

http://www.flos-freeware.ch/notepad2.html

VERY similar..
Open source, coded in c++, x86/x64
syntax highlighting and plugin support.
And very light weight and low resource usage. Notepad2 is also a Scintilla-based text editor.

Any requests for seeding/re-seeding should be posted at the forum below. You'll get a much quicker response from the uploader/s

https://forum.suprbay.org/index.php
